      <title>When Tomcat keeps throwing OutOfMemory</title>
      <link>https://kimpaper.github.io/en/posts/centos/2015-02-06-tomcat-outofmemory/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Feb 2015 17:10:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://kimpaper.github.io/en/posts/centos/2015-02-06-tomcat-outofmemory/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h4 id=&#34;add-the-following-at-the-very-top-of-catalinash-to-increase-the-memory-careful--keep-the-servers-total-memory-in-mind&#34;&gt;Add the following at the very top of catalina.sh to increase the memory. (Careful — keep the server&amp;rsquo;s total memory in mind.)&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;
&lt;table class=&#34;lntable&#34;&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&#34;lntd&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class=&#34;lntd&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-gdscript3&#34; data-lang=&#34;gdscript3&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;export&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;CATALINA_OPTS&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;-Djava.awt.headless=true -server -Xms2048m -Xmx2048m -XX:NewSize=256m -XX:MaxNewSize=256m -XX:PermSize=256m -XX:MaxPermSize=512m -XX:+CMSClassUnloadingEnabled -XX:+CMSPermGenSweepingEnabled&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Reference) &lt;a href=&#34;http://stackoverflow.com/questions/88235/dealing-with-java-lang-outofmemoryerror-permgen-space-error&#34;&gt;http://stackoverflow.com/questions/88235/dealing-with-java-lang-outofmemoryerror-permgen-space-error&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;</description>
